42
00:04:04.169 --> 00:04:07.156
Should I close my eyes?
I'd still be able to hear the music.

43
00:04:07.156 --> 00:04:09.860
- You don't want to see me?
- Yes.

44
00:04:09.860 --> 00:04:13.355
Do I suck because I gave you
a warning without knowing anything?

45
00:04:13.355 --> 00:04:15.548
- Yes.
- Are you disappointed?

46
00:04:15.548 --> 00:04:17.076
Very much.

47
00:04:20.423 --> 00:04:22.245
So So, you still have a long way to go.

48
00:04:22.937 --> 00:04:26.440
You said you followed
a man here and got married.

49
00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:27.762
Don't bring that up.

50
00:04:27.762 --> 00:04:29.839
You can't go home
now that the man is gone.

51
00:04:29.839 --> 00:04:32.446
- San Ma Ru.
- You're ashamed to see your family

52
00:04:32.446 --> 00:04:36.007
so you're getting your PhD
as if you're being punished.

53
00:04:36.959 --> 00:04:39.103
Why do you despise yourself so much?

54
00:04:41.533 --> 00:04:43.838
You said I was right
to fight against my company.

55
00:04:44.422 --> 00:04:47.290
My company is suing me
for 1.4 billion won.

56
00:04:47.290 --> 00:04:50.031
For disturbing their business
and exposing secret information.

57
00:04:54.009 --> 00:04:55.283
What do you think?

58
00:04:56.372 --> 00:05:00.358
Can you still say...
I did the right thing?

59
00:05:01.927 --> 00:05:03.377
You didn't do anything wrong.

60
00:05:03.377 --> 00:05:06.572
That's what I wanted to say.
You did nothing wrong.

61
00:05:06.572 --> 00:05:10.315
It's not wrong for you to be
hung up on your past.

62
00:05:14.045 --> 00:05:15.355
Will you sit down?

63
00:05:30.923 --> 00:05:36.237
The wrong thing to do...
would be to forget about it.

64
00:05:36.237 --> 00:05:37.985
Without any worries.

65
00:05:39.507 --> 00:05:42.105
I... just like this place.

66
00:05:42.105 --> 00:05:46.266
My job isn't bad.
I'm not forcing myself to endure it.

67
00:05:46.266 --> 00:05:48.208
What do you really want to do?

68
00:05:48.208 --> 00:05:52.439
What do you really want to say
besides telling me to go back to Korea?

69
00:05:52.439 --> 00:05:53.994
Come back to Korea.

70
00:05:55.487 --> 00:05:57.038
Are you kidding me?

71
00:05:58.771 --> 00:06:00.675
Come back to Korea and date me.

72
00:06:00.675 --> 00:06:03.086
If you go back to France
after that, I'll come to you.

73
00:06:03.086 --> 00:06:06.062
I can't come here every time.

74
00:06:06.062 --> 00:06:11.321
I mean, I can come, but I won't see
you often, and it'll be expensive.

75
00:06:11.321 --> 00:06:13.358
I'm not saying
it's a waste of money, though.

76
00:06:13.358 --> 00:06:14.985
What is this?

77
00:06:16.326 --> 00:06:17.673
A proposal.

78
00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:24.572
How can a proposal be so logical?

79
00:06:24.572 --> 00:06:26.697
I don't feel anything.

80
00:06:27.384 --> 00:06:29.004
I'm sorry.

81
00:06:29.004 --> 00:06:31.432
You ruined our date.

82
00:06:32.132 --> 00:06:33.430
About my proposal...

83
00:06:33.430 --> 00:06:36.949
There are too many things
we don't know about each other.

84
00:06:36.949 --> 00:06:41.281
- Tomorrow is our last day.
- Then, I'll answer you tomorrow.

85
00:06:41.281 --> 00:06:43.360
What will your answer be?

86
00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.367
I'll just follow my heart.

87
00:06:45.367 --> 00:06:47.430
I can't see the stage.

88
00:06:49.362 --> 00:06:50.769
Then look at me instead.

89
00:07:23.343 --> 00:07:26.872
The High-quality France Premium Package.

90
00:07:26.872 --> 00:07:28.790
Are you aware that today is the last day?

91
00:07:28.790 --> 00:07:30.067
Yes!

92
00:07:30.860 --> 00:07:32.646
You don't have to answer me.

93
00:07:32.646 --> 00:07:35.867
After we take pictures
at a special location

94
00:07:35.867 --> 00:07:39.266
we will pass Pont Neuf
and visit Place de la Concorde.

95
00:07:39.266 --> 00:07:44.689
And then we'll go to the Louvre and
Notre-Dame de Paris on this exciting day.

96
00:07:44.689 --> 00:07:49.107
I contemplated long and hard about
where to take our commemorative pictures.

97
00:07:49.107 --> 00:07:52.591
- Are you curious about the reason?
- Yes!

98
00:07:52.591 --> 00:07:55.139
You don't have to answer me.

99
00:07:55.139 --> 00:07:59.067
In most packages, the Eiffel Tower
observatory is included.

100
00:07:59.067 --> 00:08:03.418
But if you go there,
you just think, "Wow, it's high."

101
00:08:03.418 --> 00:08:06.166
It's similar to what you see
when you take off or land on a plane.

102
00:08:06.166 --> 00:08:11.322
But the place
we're going to is very different.

103
00:08:11.322 --> 00:08:15.925
It's not an observatory. But you can
see the most beautiful view of Paris.

104
00:08:18.564 --> 00:08:23.415
Did everyone fight?
Why does everyone look down?

105
00:08:23.415 --> 00:08:26.711
I guess this is a family-like
atmosphere after all.

106
00:08:26.711 --> 00:08:29.781
You know that families
fight the most, right?

107
00:08:30.355 --> 00:08:34.274
We're going to get off, so remember to
take your passports, wallets, and phones!

108
00:08:34.274 --> 00:08:35.458
Yes!

109
00:08:43.908 --> 00:08:46.687
Father, what does this place
remind you of?

110
00:08:46.687 --> 00:08:49.293
Where else? It looks like France.

111
00:08:49.293 --> 00:08:51.837
- Is it a good place to grill meat?
- No way.

112
00:08:51.837 --> 00:08:53.663
This is a classy place.

113
00:08:54.640 --> 00:08:58.259
This is the first Paris observatory.

114
00:08:58.259 --> 00:09:02.249
Take a look around,
and meet back here in 15 minutes.

115
00:09:02.249 --> 00:09:04.725
- Yes.
- Yes.

116
00:09:12.437 --> 00:09:15.964
- Let's take a picture.
- Later.

117
00:09:15.964 --> 00:09:18.879
I'm sorry. Forgive me. Do you
want me to take a picture of you?

118
00:09:18.879 --> 00:09:21.590
That's okay. I don't feel
like taking pictures.

119
00:09:21.590 --> 00:09:24.341
- Don't you know what day it is?
- Excuse me.

120
00:09:26.326 --> 00:09:27.418
I was wondering...

121
00:09:27.418 --> 00:09:30.581
Would you like a picture?
Fom the waist up?

122
00:09:30.581 --> 00:09:34.635
No, you took a good one last time,
so you can take it freely this time.

123
00:09:34.635 --> 00:09:36.964
Then, I'll make you look like
an actress this time.

124
00:09:36.964 --> 00:09:39.581
Hey, I could never be an actress.

125
00:09:39.581 --> 00:09:42.739
- Where should I stand? Here?
- Move back a bit.

126
00:09:42.739 --> 00:09:45.196
Yes, that's good. I'll take it now.

127
00:09:46.441 --> 00:09:49.187
- You're doing that again.
- What?

128
00:09:49.187 --> 00:09:52.385
- Pose in a sexy way.
- Gosh, how could I?

129
00:09:52.385 --> 00:09:54.738
- Like this?
