134
00:10:10.697 --> 00:10:14.196
Wow! You're so pretty!

135
00:10:14.196 --> 00:10:16.365
<i>Did you know?</i>

136
00:10:16.365 --> 00:10:20.672
<i>I hate the sight of you taking pictures.</i>

137
00:10:23.730 --> 00:10:25.669
Get up already! You're so stubborn!

138
00:10:25.669 --> 00:10:28.528
Just one picture.

139
00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:32.832
Why would you take a funeral photo
if we came here for a passport photo?

140
00:10:32.832 --> 00:10:36.546
- Are we dying on vacation?
- I might as well since I'm here.

141
00:10:36.546 --> 00:10:40.173
If I take it now,
he'll give me a 20 percent discount.

142
00:10:40.173 --> 00:10:41.760
Get up so we can go home!

143
00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:45.888
These days, people don't call them
funeral pictures as if it's unlucky.

144
00:10:45.888 --> 00:10:47.977
If you take it early,
you'll receive more luck...

145
00:10:47.977 --> 00:10:51.390
You're just trying to sell your
service! I want to talk to your boss!

146
00:10:51.390 --> 00:10:55.721
Fine, I won't take it. Stop it.
I won't take it. Let's go.

147
00:10:55.721 --> 00:10:58.000
- How dare you...
- I'm sorry. I'll be back.

148
00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:59.975
- Let go!
- Stop it!

149
00:10:59.975 --> 00:11:03.201
<i>It's because you only think about
dying instead of fighting to live.</i>

150
00:11:03.201 --> 00:11:04.692
<i>I had my reasons.</i>

151
00:11:04.692 --> 00:11:06.400
Don't take her funeral photo!

152
00:11:12.054 --> 00:11:14.630
- Gosh, what is this?
- It turned out well!

153
00:11:14.630 --> 00:11:17.234
Erase this one. Erase it.

154
00:11:18.481 --> 00:11:20.567
<i>You're so pretty when you smile.</i>

155
00:11:21.738 --> 00:11:24.350
<i>You're beautiful, no matter
how much I look at you.</i>

156
00:11:28.028 --> 00:11:31.269
- Come here.
- Don't boss an elder around.

157
00:11:31.269 --> 00:11:34.355
Gosh, I'll take a picture of both of you.

158
00:11:34.974 --> 00:11:37.913
You're a photographer now, huh?

159
00:11:37.913 --> 00:11:40.775
Ready? Smile!

160
00:11:42.369 --> 00:11:44.157
Mister, try to smile.

161
00:11:44.157 --> 00:11:47.572
- Hurry up.
- Ma'am, link arms.

162
00:11:52.544 --> 00:11:54.686
Mister, it'd be
so much better if you smiled!

163
00:11:54.686 --> 00:11:59.011
Big Sis, you don't listen.
You should just take it...

164
00:11:59.011 --> 00:12:00.999
Did you take it while I was talking?

165
00:12:00.999 --> 00:12:04.083
- What the heck?
- You're too much.

166
00:12:04.083 --> 00:12:05.828
It didn't turn out well.

167
00:12:07.551 --> 00:12:10.384
Let me see if it turned out well.

168
00:12:10.384 --> 00:12:12.397
She said it didn't turn out well.

169
00:12:17.990 --> 00:12:20.855
<i>They say you should refuse
the first time around.</i>

170
00:12:20.855 --> 00:12:24.464
<i>I was planning to smile
and hold your hand</i>

171
00:12:24.464 --> 00:12:26.644
<i>after the first few shots.</i>

172
00:12:37.947 --> 00:12:40.740
